### **4. 30_StreamChartPulse**  
**Description:**  
Live charting of real-time numeric input for simulation or monitoring.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamChartPulse - Real-Time Data Visualizer

StreamChartPulse takes in a live data stream and displays it as a scrolling line chart.

## Features
- Real-time rendering  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Matplotlib-based  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_StreamChartPulse.git
cd 30_StreamChartPulse
python visualize.py
